description:
Your creatures always have {CONDNAME_BUFF_SPLASH} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_SAVAGE}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_SPLASH}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_SAVAGE}

Your creatures ignore enemies' {CONDNAME_BUFF_SHELL} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_BARRIER} buffs.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_SHELL}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_BARRIER}

After an enemy takes damage from {CONDNAME_DEBUFF_BURNED}, they are afflicted with either {CONDNAME_DEBUFF_SCORN} or {CONDNAME_DEBUFF_SILENCE}.

{CONDDESC_DEBUFF_SCORN}

{CONDDESC_DEBUFF_SILENCE}

At the start of battle, your creatures gain {CONDNAME_BUFF_INVISIBLE} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_PROFICIENT}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_INVISIBLE}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_PROFICIENT}

After your creatures {ACTION_attack}, they gain {CONDNAME_BUFF_SPLASH} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_SAVAGE}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_SPLASH}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_SAVAGE}

After your creatures {ACTION_defend}, they gain {CONDNAME_BUFF_DEFENSIVE} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_REBIRTH}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_DEFENSIVE}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_REBIRTH}

After your creatures {ACTION_provoke}, they gain {CONDNAME_BUFF_TAUNT} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_PROTECT}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_TAUNT}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_PROTECT}

After your creatures take damage from a spell, they gain {CONDNAME_BUFF_REPELLING} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_SHELL}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_REPELLING}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_SHELL}

After your creatures take damage from an attack, they gain {CONDNAME_BUFF_AGILE} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_MEND}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_AGILE}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_MEND}

After one of your creatures is killed, all your creatures gain {CONDNAME_BUFF_BERSERK} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_LEECH}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_BERSERK}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_LEECH}

After an enemy takes damage from an ally, they are afflicted with {CONDNAME_DEBUFF_BLIND} and {CONDNAME_DEBUFF_CONFUSED}.

{CONDDESC_DEBUFF_BLIND}

{CONDDESC_DEBUFF_CONFUSED}

Your creatures always have {CONDNAME_BUFF_LEECH} and {CONDNAME_BUFF_MEND}.

{CONDDESC_BUFF_LEECH}

{CONDDESC_BUFF_MEND}
